OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1771851971
OL,3,CManchester actress Wunmi Mosaku wins
OL,4,CBAFTA
OL,6,FManchester actress Wunmi Mosaku has
OL,7,Fwon the BAFTA for best supporting
OL,8,Factress.
OL,10,FThe actress from Chorlton picked up
OL,11,Fthe award for her role as Annie in the
OL,12,Fmusical film Sinners.
OL,14,FShe faced a tough field of nominees,
OL,15,Fincluding fellow UK performers Carey
OL,16,FMulligan, for The Ballad Of Wallis
OL,17,FIsland, and Emily Watson, for Hamnet,
OL,18,Fas well as US actress - and bookies'
OL,19,Ffavourite - Teyana Taylor, for One
OL,20,FBattle After Another.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
