FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1771851971
OL,3,CManchester actress Wunmi Mosaku wins
OL,4,CBAFTA
OL,6,FMosaku becomes the first black British
OL,7,Fwinner of best supporting actress.
OL,9,FShe was one of the most high-profile
OL,10,Fsuccesses for the UK on a night
OL,11,Fotherwise dominated by talent from
OL,12,Fother countries.
OL,14,FThe British-Nigerian actress said she
OL,15,Fis "really grateful" for the
OL,16,Frepresentation in the highly acclaimed
OL,17,Fvampire film Sinners.
OL,26,@wD@DOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
