FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1771851971
OL,3,CManchester actress Wunmi Mosaku wins
OL,4,CBAFTA
OL,6,FSpeaking during her winner's press
OL,7,Fconference, she said the response from
OL,8,F"black women feeling seen" from her
OL,9,Frole, has made her feel a sense of
OL,10,F"kinship" to her community.
OL,12,F"It always feels good when you feel
OL,13,Flike your story and your experience is
OL,14,Fbeing represented with integrity and
OL,15,Fcreativity.
OL,17,F"Since the film came out, just seeing
OL,18,Fthe response of black women feeling
OL,19,Fseen, loved, valued, treasured, and
OL,20,Fthe power of our ancestry and the
OL,21,Fspirituality," she added.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@ZO]rD@AOUrD@IO]tD@AOUyD@AOU}D@
OL,26,ANO]
