PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1771851971
OL,3,CManchester actress Wunmi Mosaku wins
OL,4,CBAFTA
OL,6,F"For me, seeing that response made me
OL,7,Frealise how lonely I felt and all of a
OL,8,Fsudden these women were in my life who
OL,9,FI'd never met, I felt a kinship to."
OL,11,FMosaku, 39, emigrated from Nigeria to
OL,12,FManchester with her family when she
OL,13,Fwas one.
OL,15,FShe went on to attend the Trinity
OL,16,FChurch of England High School in
OL,17,FHulme, and Xaverian Sixth Form College
OL,18,Fin Rusholme before moving to London to
OL,19,Fstudy acting at the Royal Academy of
OL,20,FDramatic Art (RADA).
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@dO]
