PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1771851971
OL,3,CManchester actress Wunmi Mosaku wins
OL,4,CBAFTA
OL,6,FFollowing her Oscar nomination, which
OL,7,Fwas announced in January, Xavarian
OL,8,FCollege posted on social media to wish
OL,9,Fher luck, saying: "We wish her lots of
OL,10,Fluck at the forthcoming Oscars
OL,11,Fceremony and hope she can add an Oscar
OL,12,Fto the may awards she has already won."
OL,14,FThe breakthrough role for the actress
OL,15,Fcame in 2009 as she played Joy in the
OL,16,Fmini-series Moses Jones.
OL,18,FMosaku won a Bafta TV Award in 2017
OL,19,Ffor best supporting actress for her
OL,20,Frole as Gloria Taylor in Damilola, Our
OL,21,FLoved Boy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
