FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1771851971
OL,3,CManchester actress Wunmi Mosaku wins
OL,4,CBAFTA
OL,6,FIn her acceptance speech, the star
OL,7,Fsaid: "Thank you Bafta for this
OL,8,Fincredible honour.
OL,10,F"To my daughter, you are my greatest
OL,11,Fteacher. I am so proud of you,
OL,12,Feverything begins and ends with you."
OL,14,FReferencing her role in the highly
OL,15,Facclaimed vampire film, Mosaku said:
OL,16,F"I found a part of myself in Annie, a
OL,17,Fpart of my hopes, my ancestral power
OL,18,Fand connection, parts I thought I had
OL,19,Flost or tried to dim as an immigrant
OL,20,Ftrying to fit in."
OL,26,@oD@GOUrD@AOUtD@eO]xD@AOU|D@RO]
